textContent:
---so sweet---

Hi my bby!! I miss you so much!! Night shift-ish (kase nga hinahati ko pa HAHAHA) nako and I just want you kahapon and kagabi for spending your whole day with me nung pumunta tayo Manila and for also forcing yourself to stay awake para lang makasama ako huhu. 

I love you so much bby!! I appreciate you super! 

You make everything better for me and your presence alone is enough to make my mood better. I'm so lucky to have you bby! If not for you, yesterday would've been so much more different. Sad boy nako na naka pout non kase di ko kasama bbycakes ko HUHUHUHU. I love every moment that I spend with you and I keep looking back to those moments lalong lalo na namimiss kita ngayon.
